# This fixture needs a real (hand-authored, never `npm install`ed)
# node_modules with bin-less manifests, so pre-install bin conservatism does
# NOT blanket-keep every unreferenced dependency alive — that would mask the
# capacitor-platform-dependency rule under test. The repo-root .gitignore
# excludes every "node_modules/" directory; these negations re-include only this
# fixture's own hand-authored one.
!node_modules/
!node_modules/**
